/>\n<br />\n即係咩？<br />\n<br />\n即係每多一個sms 都多一份月尾比屋企人屌到飛起既風險<br />\n<br />\n但果陣理得你啦 唔通唔send咩<br />\n<br />\n但sms最好既係 <br />\n<br />\n你唔知對方有冇睇<br />\n<br />\n唔知對方有冇online用電話<br />\n<br />\n唔知對方係咪輸入中<br />\n<br />\n但我地兩個永遠好珍惜每一個sms<br />\n<br />\n每一個sms都用個心 用時間去打一大段野出黎<br />\n<br />\n一無野做就打開部電話睇下對方覆左未<br />\n<br />\n當然如果大家都係屋企就會用facebook 傾計<br />\n<br />\n但後來我都忍唔住偷偷地開一張人仔台卡同佢send<br />\n<br />\n但已經太遲了 月尾張單 好似係400幾500蚊？<br />\n<br />\n真係好快好快 我地既sms就愈黎愈曖昧<br />\n<br />\n慢慢了解得多 我發覺佢既美唔單止係外表既美<br />\n<br />\n談吐得體有教養 同時又好pure 好true<br />\n<br />\n[我在炫耀　你的美好 疊起了完美的宇宙]<br />\n<br />\n至於我地傾計既內容係咩？<br />\n<br />\n唔重要啦<br />\n<br />\n但我記得<br />\n<br />\n佢好鐘意好鐘意羅力威<br />\n<br />\n我就鐘意陳奕迅既<br />\n<br />\n對話內容就係呢首歌入面啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h3sEYBYqc1g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dh3sEYBYqc1g&d=5MQD4pzSAkkJjZBrjouuh6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=a46df243\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h3sEYBYqc1g</a>"},{"pid":"0aae3e8c6cfa191c45ea744384ca69926a7db1fa","tid":612506,"uid":25582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:54:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知有幾多人有興趣睇我回憶<br />\n不過都好想打落去 想幫自己呢個故事結尾"},{"pid":"8d0b320b0b786ae8c2120293a7ec584d302603a9","tid":612506,"uid":139346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:56:31.000Z","msg":"追緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee0eb598e325eb9a4571117fbe5bb481cc8135a","tid":612506,"uid":135577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c0b21f89f0f54cff3305e0a0004e3a70f707128","tid":612506,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"90d9a12b954d9d63d65afbfd7aff20fe45cd283e","tid":612506,"uid":83440,"lik